1. *Pretnja* može biti verbalna ili fizička. (Threat can be verbal or physical.)
2. Policija je primila *pretnju* poštom. (The police received a threat by mail.)
3. Ponašanje nekih zaposlenih predstavlja *pretnju* za bezbednost firme. (The behavior of some employees poses a threat to the company's security.)
4. Ovaj virus je *pretnja* zdravlju ljudi širom sveta. (This virus is a threat to people's health worldwide.)
5. Ukoliko se nešto ne preduzme, to će predstavljati veliku *pretnju* za ekonomiju. (If nothing is done, it will pose a great threat to the economy.)
6. *Pretnja* se odnosila na celu porodicu. (The threat was directed at the entire family.)
7. Nema mesta za *pretnje* i nasilje u bilo kom obliku. (There is no place for threats and violence in any form.)
8. Poslodavac je koristio *pretnje* kako bi primorao radnike da rade prekovremeno. (The employer used threats to force employees to work overtime.)
9. Potrebno je ozbiljno shvatiti *pretnju* terorizma. (It is necessary to take the threat of terrorism seriously.)
10. Njegovo ponašanje predstavlja *pretnju* po njega same. (His behavior poses a threat to himself.)